azy" width="1096" height="617" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/hoshimachi_suisei_imagr_2d_2022.jpg" alt="星町水成" class="wp-image-83152"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Suisei Hoshimachi 图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp. </figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="102154" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/hoshimachi-suisei-became-the-5th-active-vtuber-in-japan-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/hoshimachi_suisei_youtube_subscribers_2m/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hoshimachi_suisei_youtube_subscribers_2m.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="hoshimachi_suisei_youtube_subscribers_2m" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hoshimachi_suisei_youtube_subscribers_2m.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hoshimachi_suisei_youtube_subscribers_2m.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/hoshimachi_suisei_youtube_subscribers_2m.png" alt="" class="wp-image-102154"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：YouTube<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p>这是第10位VTuber人才（包括现役、暂停、毕业、退役人才）。星町先生所属的Hololive Productions的第8位成员。这是她出道后第2015天录制的，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">她是第一位拥有200万订阅者的前/独立（个人）虚拟歌手</span>。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="102158" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/hoshimachi-suisei-became-the-5th-active-vtuber-in-japan-to-re